{"pageContext":{"group":[{"node":{"id":"2af9bf47-85fb-5e12-a754-1b944dec8931","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-7","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 7","date":"2017-12-04T13:36:11.000Z","excerpt":"<p>This week I have brought together 6 links that cover design, code and process. Some great pieces of inspiration as well as some hopefully useful snippets to enhance your work. &nbsp; Website Design Example A brief look at the new website for Heydays from Oslo. Its nice. Its simple. I like it. Also, its pretty [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/3b7c4/Heydays-new-website.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/03841/Heydays-new-website.jpg 250w,\n/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/26396/Heydays-new-website.jpg 500w,\n/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/3b7c4/Heydays-new-website.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"Heydays new website","alt_text":"Heydays new website"},"categories":[{"name":"Branding"},{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"UX"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Design System"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Photoshop"},{"name":"Snippets"},{"name":"Trends"},{"name":"UX"}]}},{"node":{"id":"8e4e033b-aaf4-5e24-867a-6cd018f1c54e","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-6","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 6","date":"2017-11-28T10:15:54.000Z","excerpt":"<p>This weeks list is more design focused, with a story telling script thrown in for good measure. As most design/dev sites are shouting about Cyber Monday deals, I wanted to keep this on the same track as we started. I hope you enjoy. &nbsp; Designercize Needing to flex your design muscles? A little down time [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/3b7c4/YELLOW.jpg","srcSet":"/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/03841/YELLOW.jpg 250w,\n/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/26396/YELLOW.jpg 500w,\n/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/3b7c4/YELLOW.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"YELLOW","alt_text":"An example of yellow websites"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Ramblings"}],"tags":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Storytelling"},{"name":"Type"},{"name":"Yellow"}]}},{"node":{"id":"33a09e38-75d8-5d09-b045-a1b22a1e0356","slug":"creative-and-development-inspiration-5-feature-highlights","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 5: Feature Highlights","date":"2017-11-20T13:19:07.000Z","excerpt":"<p>Finding ways to display hidden information for users can be tough. The number of times brochure websites have required some level of user engagement and I have had to scour the web for examples such as these. I thought I should share. &nbsp; Project Feature Highlights By adding tooltips into div elements they can be positioned anywhere [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.9569471624266144,"src":"/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/1a92f/hover-tooltip.jpg","srcSet":"/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/788f9/hover-tooltip.jpg 250w,\n/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/06f71/hover-tooltip.jpg 500w,\n/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/1a92f/hover-tooltip.jpg 1000w","sizes":"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"}}},"title":"Hover Tooltip Header","alt_text":"Animated button tooltips"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"General Coding"}],"tags"